Module com.example.project3
Package com.example.project3

Class Savings

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3.Account
com.example.project3.Savings
Direct Known Subclasses:
MoneyMarket
public class Savings
extends Account
Savings class extends Account class and creates a savings account with the given interest rate and fees. Using Account abstract class, it can get account type, fee, and interest rate.
Author:
Sebastian Carrasco, Rachael Chin
